    "BEYOND 5G TECHNOLOGYImplementing CPS using technologies beyond 5G is an appealing choice for various application domains.",
    "However, there are several challenges associated with it.The network architectures of beyond 5G involve more distributed networks, which increases system complexity and necessitates significant investments in network infrastructure (Bandi, 2022; Bandi & Yalamarthi, 2022).",
    "Moreover, effective data management is another hurdle as future CPS requires efficient systems for data collection, processing, storage, analysis, and visualization.",
    "Developing such systems to handle complex and larger datasets is costly.",
    "Since beyond 5G technology is still in its early stages of development, there is no established standardization framework for it, making it crucial to ensure compatibility and interoperability among different systems."
  ],
